{"tid":2040031,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台部署機動導彈車反制解放軍","createTime":"2020-05-28T10:19:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T10:56:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"305bb6534737414c6f50a0f50321f8b89dbd6d7a","tid":2040031,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:19:20.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200528/IP22B4ZFVUL4BAMVFJKRTOBVHI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200528%2FIP22B4ZFVUL4BAMVFJKRTOBVHI%2F&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLu2lERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=143b1fe4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200528%2FIP22B4ZFVUL4BAMVFJKRTOBVHI%2F&h=90ebceef\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200528/IP22B4ZFVUL4BAMVFJKRTOBVHI/</a><br />\n<br />\n台部署機動導彈車反制解放軍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BI3QVBI4N5AMONMMQ5UWCHFSHE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBI3QVBI4N5AMONMMQ5UWCHFSHE.jpg&h=bdc757d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台軍部署雄風導彈機動發射車反制解放軍。<br />\n<br />\n解放軍航母及軍艦編隊繞台頻繁，並將於今年8月派出雙航母參與演習。台灣國防部昨日首度公佈反制措施，將在2023年完成建構全台雄風反艦導彈機動發射車91輛，國軍可依據實際戰場需求，利用其機動性提高存活率，及增加聯合制海戰術運用彈性。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n構成全島反艦攻擊網<br />\n<br />\n台灣海軍的「機動導彈車」專案總預算近137億新台幣（下同，約35.4億港元）。根據規劃，將由中科院發展第二代岸基機動式反艦導彈系統，提高制海作戰能力，同時強化雄風二型、雄風三型反艦導彈的岸基機動發射系統外，還強調戰鬥力保存與強化通情指控能力，構成全島反艦導彈的攻擊網。<br />\n<br />\n「海鋒」機動中隊現役的陸基型雄風二型反艦導彈，可在發。。。。。。。。。。達的偵察，射程達150公里，對解放軍航母編隊及艦隊都有相當大嚇阻力。<br />\n<br />\n根據書面報告，海軍的計劃於2017年至2023年將完成雄風二型箱組導彈產製36枚、雄二飛彈壽限件換裝50枚，另有91輛機動車組車輛。車輛可視乎實際戰場需求，利用其。。。。。。。。。。劃預計會耗資25.5億元（約6.6億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n另外，解放軍計劃8月在海南島周邊進行奪島、登陸演習，並以目前由。。。。。。。。。。部人士，指共軍航母戰鬥群將會通過東沙島，前往菲律賓海演習。<br />\n<br />\n台灣蘋果新聞網"},{"pid":"43b2d54c956c6bf9b55464c152c92766dda4dbdf","tid":2040031,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:42:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"925180c3cee980c97a56788e4af4a6547424eb8d","tid":2040031,"uid":202079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:44:20.000Z","msg":"2023年先得91架發射車，夠唔夠用架?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da693d00319ce2641cb2952e90d3063b089d9c9a","tid":2040031,"uid":37912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:56:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}